<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Book Deleted Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #fff;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #c57a45;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .book-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .book-details p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello {{received_by}},</h2>

    <p>We wanted to inform you that your book has been deleted from our platform. Here are the details of the book:</p>

    <div class="book-details">
      <p><strong>Title:</strong> {{book_title}}</p>
      <p><strong>Author:</strong> {{book_author}}</p>
      <p><strong>Category:</strong> {{book_category}}</p>
      {{#if book_price}}
        <p><strong>Price:</strong> â‚¹{{book_price}}</p>
      {{/if}}
      {{#if book_publish_date}}
        <p><strong>Publish Date:</strong> {{book_publish_date}}</p>
      {{/if}}
    </div>

    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{current_year}} Readify. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
